sections.text:
(a) Unless the terms of a trust provide otherwise, the rules applicable to a trustee apply to a trust director regarding the following matters:

(1) Acceptance under § 19-1307.01;

(2) Giving of bond to secure performance under § 19-1307.02;

(3) Reasonable compensation under § 19-1307.08;

(4) Resignation under § 19-1307.05;

(5) Removal under § 19-1307.06; and

(6) Vacancy and appointment of successor under § 19-1307.04.
